The Talented Mr. Ripley;;80;;83;;R;;To be young and carefree amid the blue waters and idyllic landscape of sun-drenched Italy in the late 1950s; that's la dolce vita Tom Ripley (Matt Damon) craves- and Dickie Greenleaf (Jude Law) leads. When Dickie's father asks Tom to bring his errant playboy son back home to America, Dickie and his beautiful expatriate girlfriend, Marge Sherwood (Gwyneth Paltrow), never suspect the dangerous extremes to which Ripley will go to make their lifestyle his own.;;Mystery & thriller,Crime,Drama;;Anthony Minghella;;1999;;Matt Damon,Gwyneth Paltrow,Jude Law,Cate Blanchett,Philip Seymour Hoffman,Jack Davenport,James Rebhorn,Sergio Rubini,Philip Baker Hall,Celia Weston,Rosario Fiorello,Stefania Rocca,Ivano Marescotti,Anna Longhi,Alessandro Fabrizi,Lisa Eichhorn;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/talented_mr_ripley